Write a java program to find reverse of a string in java?
Step1.Input a String.
Step2.Take one String name it Reverse and initialze it empty:String reverseString=""
Step3.Extract last character from input string and put it in reverseString.
Step4.Finally print reverse String.

:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
package io.javabrains;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class ReversingString {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Scanner scan = new Scanner(System.in);
		System.out.println("Enter input String:- ");
		String inputString = scan.nextLine();
		String reverseString = "";
		System.out.println("String before Reverse: " + inputString);
		for (int i = inputString.length()-1; i >= 0; i--) {
			reverseString = reverseString + inputString.charAt(i);
		}
		System.out.println("String after Reverse: " + reverseString);

	}
}

:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

Enter input String:- 
Cognizant Technology Solutions
String before Reverse: Cognizant Technology Solutions
String after Reverse: snoituloS ygolonhceT tnazingoC
